\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\f0\fs22\lang9 Welcome to \ldblquote Machine Learning Models \f1\endash  Learning from models to make predictions.\rdblquote  After watching this video, you will be able to define a machine learning model, describe the different learning model types, and describe how to use a learning model to solve a problem. Now data contains a wealth of information that can be used to solve certain types of problems. Traditional data analysis approaches can be a person manually inspecting the data or a specialized computer program that automates the human analysis. These approaches reach their limits due to the amount of data to be analyzed or the complexity of the problem. Machine learning (ML) uses algorithms \endash  also known as \ldblquote models\rdblquote  - to identify patterns in the data. The process by which the model learns these patterns from data is called \ldblquote model training\rdblquote .\par
